FBIS4-55654 "dreeu097_d_94005" FBIS-EEU-94-097 Daily Report 18 May 1994 SLOVAKIA Party Rejects KDH Offer Party Rejects KDH Offer LD1805221294 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1630 GMT 18 May 94 LD1805221294 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network in Slovak 1630 GMT 18 May 94 Slovak BFN [Text] The Party of Businessmen and Tradesmen has rejected the offer made by the Christian Democratic Movement [KDH] to allow certain right-wing forces to stand on the KDH party ticket in elections. Party officials reached this decision following a meeting today with KDH Chairman Jan Carnogursky. According to them, the seats they were offered to run for could not be won.
